  "signal_description": "The query retrieves the number of cases, the average cycle time, and the material group text for purchase order items. It is performed on the 'defaultview-124' table. The 'No. of Cases' column represents the count of unique case IDs. The 'Avg. Cycle Time' column calculates the average time difference between the 'END_TIME' of the 'Create FI Invoice' event and the 'END_TIME' of the 'Create Goods Receipt' event. The 'PO Item Material Group Text' column contains the text description of the material group for each purchase order item. The results are grouped by the 'PO Item Material Group Text' column, sorted in descending order based on the 'No. of Cases' column, and limited to 50 rows."
}
